Author: xoxoemogrlxoxo
Text: I don’t know if it’s the capillaries that break, the gross food that comes up from the toilet, or my body reacting to vomiting or even the food! I don’t purge often but when I have, I also get acne.

Author: coolcat411
Text: For sure! Even if I haven’t purged in days my skin usually stays pretty shitty until it’s been a while without. I think it also correlated with what I’m eating before I purge - sugars, fats, etc.  I wish it was enough to stop :(
